stores.description:
Kashyapi Naturals & Organic Foods is born with a vision to provide 100% chemical-free food at honest prices and premium quality.

We are passionate about natural farming and practice SPNF (Sri Subhash Palekar Natural Farming) based farming in our own farm, Kashyapi SPNF Farm near Kanakapura. We use only native cow dung and cow urine and prepare all the required fertilizers/pesticides like Jeevamrutha, Dashaparani, Neemasthra, Agniasthra, etc ourselves.  We are connected to many Natural/SPNF farmers group throughout India and procure chemical-free produce directly from them and sell in our own store. Hence, you are not only assured of best quality chemical-free food but also assured of its best price.

Kashyapi Naturals is not just any other Organic Food Store but a specialized Organic boutique Food Store, where only trusted and authentic products, personally validated by us for its quality and authenticity are available under one roof. Hence, you can close your eyes and buy products without worrying which brand to purchase. We truly believe that Kashyapi Store is a platform where we serve our customers with 100% chemical-free food and make difference in their lives as we strongly believe that eating good food makes you healthy and wealthy.

We have everything from Farm Fresh Organic Vegetables, Fruits, A2 Milk & Dairy , Chemical-free Cosmetics, Organic Groceries, Cold-pressed Oils, A2 Cow Ghee, Ayurvedic & Herbal products, Healthy Snacks, Ready to Eat, Rice Mix & Masala Powders, Handicrafts and many more products that is 100% natural and chemical-free to help you lead a healthy and balanced life.

Order Online or visit our physical store. We offer free delivery above тВ╣1000 order value(within 6 kms)
